author: asianlego
title: Good for starters.
review: This set is very useful especially if you're low on bricks and need some unique pieces. This set has two limited edition vehicle bonnet slope bricks printed with the words Turbo on one and a cheetah's face on the other. It also has some flags, a rare green tinted windshield. The Max and Tina figurines can be linked to those from the 4+ and Jack Stone series.
